### Quick note about IDs

When you add these 5 coaches in an empty DB, IDs will auto-generate like:

* C001, C002, C003, C004, C005
  But even if the numbering differs, it’s fine—the UI shows **coach names**.

If you want, I can also give you a **one-time Python seeding script** that inserts all 5 coaches + writes their `.md` files automatically (so you don’t have to paste manually).
